  "why_it_failed_measured": [
   "Step-1 confirmed the edge-ISI signature (dc0 SER per Q=4 segment, ema0.6: m5 [0.732, 0.604, 0.382, 0.348]; gerr [101, 85, 58, 53] deg) -- the KILL gate did NOT trigger; the mechanism's premise is real.",
   "Decision-directed adaptation at ~40% dc0 SER is SELF-POISONING (measured on m5 frame 0, ema0.6 Q4, no-revert probe): truth-free decision-EVM improves 26.8->24.6 deg across 3 iterations while TRUE dc0 SER worsens 0.397->0.529 -- the confident-error trap x10_forensics_errors documented now measured to defeat the eigen/MVDR weight solver itself. The truth-free per-carrier revert cannot catch it because the visible metric (EVM) improves.",
   "Even GENIE rotations (truth-fed reference, upper bound) only reach dc0 SER 0.343 vs 0.397 uniform on the probe frame: within-window segment reweighting is PHYSICALLY capped far above late-window (0.13 @ +32) because the echo cure requires samples BEYOND the original Nw window -- a shifted window is not in the span of partial sums of the unshifted window. The plan's 'strict superset of window placement' rationale is measurably false for within-window partial-FFT.",
   "The cw improvements pfft DID produce (m6: 19->10 on ema0.7:Q4:block vs its base fe; m5: 2->0 on ema0.6:Q4:slide64) come from clean mid/top carriers (honest covariances at 1-5% SER), not from dc0 -- same axis the alpha sweep already exploits, and fully subsumed by the late-window baseline."
